summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 2.6°C) and outside temperature (up 2.2°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 6%).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 415 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in rainfall (down 0.2 mm) and cloud levels (up 826 m) when compared to today.
